features: Cute Design: The hand dustpan tabletop brush with a little bear-shaped design in 2 colors blue and pink. The bristles belong to the soft series, suitable for cleaning dust, light and small items, etc. The lovely little bear accompanies you to make cleaning happier.

Mini Broom and Dustpan Set: This cleaning tool set includes a mini hand broom and dustpan. This dustpan has a sloped shovelhead to make your cleaning more convenient and the edge of the dustpan is close to the desktop at 0°, seamless, does not leak dust, improves your cleaning efficiency, and makes housework easier.

Quality Material: The small cleaning tools broom and dustpan are made of plastic that can be used in a kitchen, home, or office. The dustpan handle broom has soft bristles that are fit for sweeping and cleaning up dust from your floor. The soft and long-lasting durable bristles help attract dirt effectively by brushing them into the mini dustpan.

Easy to Storage: The mini dustpan and brush set snap into the dustpan design for easy storage and cleaning. The brush head with the dustpan has a hook at the end, which is convenient for storage and does not take up space. The dustpan's size is about 20.9 x 15.9cm / 8.22 x 6.25 inches, and the size of the brush is about 18.5 x 13 cm / 7.28 x 5.11 inches. It is an ideal gift for kids' mini housekeeping that develops children's good habit of cleaning.

Multifunctional Cleaning Set: This dustpan and brush can handle large and small clutter anywhere in your home or office. Suitable for cleaning keyboards, closets, cupboard crevices, sofas, car vents and dashboards, tables, desks, window sill crevices, cat litter, and other hard-to-clean places, a good helper in your daily life.
